[quote=“Artorias, post:6, topic:550054”][quote author=cowo8 link=topic=668932.msg4473556#msg4473556 date=1424483235]

Kieran lost interest in RSWebclients and RSPS so he decided to shut it down. If you were familiar with that staff, I was Ace (Administrator)

Yea it was. Kieran left a message on the site for a couple weeks saying why he was shutting it down.[/quote]
